Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.33,0:00:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,New Himuka lied to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.54,0:00:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Seto, you know this better than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.33,0:00:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.75,0:00:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you took part in horrible experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.75,0:00:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Experiments? Explain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.83,0:00:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Gemma, we are out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.21,0:00:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We must fight for our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.25,0:00:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best that I retreat now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.88,0:01:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-Are you all right, Kasane?\N-I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.08,0:01:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Our comrades are killing each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.08,0:01:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.00,0:01:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, we always trained together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.46,0:01:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That was why we almost didn't make it\Nto the enlistment ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.38,0:01:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, would you like to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.33,0:01:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,SCARLET NEXUS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.21,0:02:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♪A crime in reality♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.54,0:02:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♪For Heaven's sake♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.79,0:02:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Accepts any fake♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.75,0:02:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♪And disappears piling the eternity in fantasy♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.29,0:02:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Won't take it at all, I get sick♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.67,0:02:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♪A girl looking back♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.71,0:02:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Casts the miracle into the instant world♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.04,0:02:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Did you lie♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.00,0:02:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Did you lie♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.88,0:02:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Spit the venom♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I know why♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I've found a game of ecstasy♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Red Criminal gets life♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I've never been in love♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.42,0:02:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Don’t know when I started\Ngetting sick of this world♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.21,0:02:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♪We will fly♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.88,0:02:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Someday I won't be crying♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I've been sacrificing myself\Nnot to hurt anybody♪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,RED STRINGS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you one of Major General Karen's men?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, don't disappoint me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.54,0:03:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what the Major General's plan it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But I will never betray my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You never tell me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.00,0:03:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think so little of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,For a righteous man like yourself\Nto act so recklessly,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.46,0:04:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,you must be very lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what rumors have reached your ears,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.54,0:04:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but is this really how you want to end it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I only seek the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Fighting my own friends
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.71,0:04:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,really sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He was acting weird before we got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He seemed to think...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.04,0:04:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomi was killed in action.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:04:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi, you saw it with your own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you say
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomi died in that battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.71,0:05:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.92,0:05:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.67,0:05:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomi is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.46,0:05:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomi was turned into an Other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I must exterminate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.04,0:05:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:05:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:05:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito! Kasane!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Seto...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-No.\N-Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"ANOMALY DETECTED"\NHis power is spiking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me that look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You will spend your life in regret\Nif you kill Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.33,0:07:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.38,0:07:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't die just yet
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi, you're my subordinate too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:07:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not let you go...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Seto...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not let go of the Red Strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.88,0:08:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, what is happening now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no clue either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is unprecedented.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.96,0:08:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.92,0:08:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.54,0:08:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this sensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.04,0:09:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.00,0:09:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did Yuito go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's leave, it's too dangerous out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, Kasane!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-Save me, Major General!\N-Major General!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.46,0:10:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Gemma!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're safe now, Lieutenant Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Seto...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Seto, sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.63,0:11:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could say so, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.13,0:11:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Captain Seto?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He was taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So Yuito and Kasane are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't feel right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.08,0:12:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.42,0:13:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.79,0:13:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But judging by the crest,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,it's from the Sumeragi family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like Yakumo Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw this in a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.75,0:13:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.46,0:14:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.83,0:14:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito! You're finally awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.33,0:14:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were taken too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.92,0:14:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.58,0:14:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are Kasane and Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.21,0:14:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.71,0:14:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do anything to help them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Had Luka not saved us just now,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.58,0:14:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,we would have been taken too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Luka?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He went looking for Major General Karen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're safe, Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Gemma isn't our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a grave mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Gemma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.13,0:15:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's check out this store\Nwhen the alert is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This place looks nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.29,0:15:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And the operation hour is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.13,0:15:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.50,0:15:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-We can't connect to the network.\N-No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.04,0:15:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-How did this happen?\N-What caused this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.17,0:15:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thankfully, my house is near a shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to have done this a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was very weak when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I often fell sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I treated my own injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.50,0:15:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're amazing. I couldn't even do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.63,0:16:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Although my uncle is\Nthe Chairman of OSF Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a mild fever. Take these pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.21,0:16:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.13,0:16:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you talk to him\Nas if nothing had happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.92,0:16:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't forgive Gemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Seto died
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.29,0:16:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,because of Gemma's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.08,0:16:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell us the whole story.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The New Himuka Government
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.29,0:16:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,used Suoh Capital as a center
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to conduct social management.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Social management?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.08,0:16:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Using physical exam as a front,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.50,0:16:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the government finds those with power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.17,0:17:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Once they were recruited into OSF,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"COMPATIBLE"\Nthere would be no way for them to say refuse it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you're in the force, your growth\Nwill be suppressed to maintain your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone knows that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.46,0:17:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.04,0:17:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I know they employed this method\Nso we could defeat the Others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is more to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.17,0:17:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know about the rehabilitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I once had a friend
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.92,0:17:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,who changed into a completely different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.54,0:17:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He used to criticize the system.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.17,0:17:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So everyone started saying
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,he had undergone the rehabilitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How could that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You are new, so you didn't know\Nabout the stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it has happened many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.25,0:18:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Rehabilitation is basically an open secret\Nthat we all know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.25,0:18:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi, you heard about it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The government was undoubtedly behind all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging by Nagi's behavior,\Nthey must have done it to him too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.33,0:18:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My actual age is 54 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon enough, the growth suppression\Nwill wear off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My body will age, and my power will become weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.58,0:18:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I will have no choice but to retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.88,0:18:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But before that,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.67,0:18:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope to learn the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.75,0:18:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when Karen told me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that Seto had taken part in the rehabilitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Seto would never do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.71,0:19:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. Why didn't I believe him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.58,0:19:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.96,0:19:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean Major General Karen
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is against New Himuka's method?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.21,0:19:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There seems to be some inside story to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.21,0:19:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen's true plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.38,0:19:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,must be something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Sumeragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.29,0:20:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A large number of Others are invading\Ncentral Suoh Capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.33,0:20:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.75,0:20:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Eradicate them immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.71,0:20:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But our defense system is not working.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.13,0:20:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Psynet is offline as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.00,0:20:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the council?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.21,0:20:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't contact them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.75,0:20:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that Arahabaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.71,0:20:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen, how did it turn out this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.83,0:20:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I will retrieve it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:20:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.04,0:21:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.08,0:21:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.58,0:21:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.46,0:21:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Kunad Highway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.33,0:21:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.17,0:21:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.58,0:21:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what we see when we woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.46,0:22:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.21,0:22:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I don't need to let fate dictate me♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.88,0:22:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Because I believe that I can rewrite it♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.58,0:22:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I'll always be a dreamer now and forever♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.08,0:23:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Another sunrise shines now and it blacks out♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.63,0:23:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♪What's waiting for us at the world's end♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.71,0:23:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Forever eternal, keep the fire going♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.71,0:23:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Who can shake us♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.08,0:23:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Who can define us♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.50,0:23:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♪It's nothing less than our story♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.46,0:23:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Forever eternal,\Nkeep the fire going in your heart♪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.21,0:24:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,KAREN'S BETRAYAL
